description: Financially, we are all a little different. Most of us need a little extra help from time to time, but where do we turn? We don't all have a rich uncle to ask for money. The truth is that there are many ways to get cash when you need it. In fact, there were so many that we took the best 101 ideas and compiled them just for you. With this guide you can save, earn, and pay for what you want when you want. Don’t be a slave to your bills and debt and make the word “broke” disappear from your vocabulary. Learn the tricks to making easy money when you need it, download the 101 Ways to Emergency Cash ebook and start earning today!
